Install PHP Globally on your pc

Then created and intiated a new project through composer

Entered these lines in to the composer
$ mkdir test-project
$ cd test-project
$ composer init

Follow the init prompt and fill out details as needed

We then take the test classes enterting this code into your classes

<?php

namespace Zubair\TestProject;

use PHPUnit\Framework\TestCase;

final class UserTest extends TestCase
{
    // Tests will go here
}

Then we ran each class seperatly through the composer to test them using this line
$ ./vendor/bin/phpunit --verbose tests/UserTest.php
